name: martini time mini notes
description:
Having a Girls night out and want to send invites? Or want to send a funky little note to one of the girls?!

	Set of 3 handmade mini note cards embellished with paper, rhinestones & funky martini stickers!

	These cards are created with super-heavy cardstock and are blank inside for your writing needs! They also come with envelopes made from colourful patterned paper.

	Deliciously packaged for gift giving or to keep for yourself! :)

	Thanks for looking! Have a lovely day. <3
